MAN.EXAMPLE:
//evaluation of a polynomial for a vector of numbers P=poly(1:3,'x') horner(P,[1 2 5]) horner(P,[1 2 5]+%i)
//evaluation of a rational s=poly(0,'s');M=[s,1/s]; horner(M,1) horner(M,%i) horner(M,1/s)
//evaluation of a polynomial for a matrix of numbers X= [1 2;3 4] p=poly(1:3,'x','c') m=horner(p, X) 1*X.^0+2*X.^1+3*X.^2
